  "informal_statement": "The midpoint ((x1+x2)/2, (y1+y2)/2) is equidistant from the two endpoints of the segment.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "The squared distances from the midpoint to each endpoint are equal polynomials; `ring`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem midpoint_equidist (x1 y1 x2 y2 : ℝ) : ((x1 + x2) / 2 - x1) ^ 2 + ((y1 + y2) / 2 - y1) ^ 2 = ((x1 + x2) / 2 - x2) ^ 2 + ((y1 + y2) / 2 - y2) ^ 2",
